# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:9
translate spanish dana2_5cfb9131:

    # "It's a fairly normal day of work. I work in Mrs. Mills office all day."
    "Es un día de trabajo bastante normal. Trabajo en la oficina de la Sra. Mills todo el día."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:10
translate spanish dana2_85a4b54e:

    # "Cleaning all the normal things."
    "Limpiando todo lo de siempre."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:12
translate spanish dana2_f50e7708:

    # "Typing all normal stuff."
    "Escribiendo todo lo de siempre."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:13
translate spanish dana2_d80566b6:

    # "Work passes quickly and I'm busy the entire time."
    "El trabajo pasa rápido y estoy ocupado todo el tiempo."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:16
translate spanish dana2_1dfeab57:

    # bs "Thanks for all your help today, [pcname]. You did good work today."
    bs "Gracias por toda tu ayuda hoy, [pcname]. Has hecho un buen trabajo hoy."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:17
translate spanish dana2_e8ce3674:

    # pc "Thank you Mrs. Mills."
    pc "Gracias, Sra. Mills."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:18
translate spanish dana2_ed5736f0:

    # bs "I'm going to stay around a little later. You have a good evening."
    bs "Me voy a quedar un rato más. Que pases una buena tarde."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:19
translate spanish dana2_dd07e1d2:

    # pc "Okay, you too Mrs. Mills."
    pc "Vale, usted también, Sra. Mills."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:20
translate spanish dana2_fe768c71:

    # "I leave her office and start walking down the hall towards the lobby."
    "Salgo de su oficina y empiezo a caminar por el pasillo hacia el vestíbulo."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:25
translate spanish dana2_e92ba526:

    # "Dana's voice stops me in my tracks. She's arguing with somebody on the phone and sounds upset."
    "La voz de Dana me detiene en seco. Está discutiendo con alguien por teléfono y parece enfadada."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:26
translate spanish dana2_1edbfb68:

    # "I don't really mean to eavesdrop, but I also don't want to just walk in on their conversation, so I lean against the wall and wait."
    "No es mi intención escuchar a escondidas, pero tampoco quiero interrumpir su conversación, así que me apoyo contra la pared y espero."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:27
translate spanish dana2_506f8528:

    # cw "I'm sorry. I'm just like ten minutes late, but I'm coming home soon, I promise."
    cw "Lo siento. Llego unos diez minutos tarde, pero voy a casa enseguida, te lo prometo."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:28
translate spanish dana2_594beb0b:

    # "There is a pause. I can hear a voice on the other side of the phone yelling, but I can't make out the words."
    "Hay una pausa. Oigo una voz al otro lado del teléfono gritando, pero no distingo las palabras."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:29
translate spanish dana2_29f965e7:

    # cw "I try to! It's not that easy. I can't just leave my work half-finished."
    cw "¡Lo intento! No es tan fácil. No puedo dejar mi trabajo a medias."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:30
translate spanish dana2_011812d0:

    # "Her voice drops and catches in her throat."
    "Su voz se apaga y se le quiebra en la garganta."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:31
translate spanish dana2_3ae30315:

    # voice dana_trying
    # cw "I'm trying. I'm sorry."
    voice dana_trying
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:33
translate spanish dana2_8788608a:

    # cw "No, I'm not cheating on you. I don't know how many times I have to tell you that."
    cw "No, no te estoy engañando. No sé cuántas veces tengo que decírtelo."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:34
translate spanish dana2_d0c4854a:

    # "More yelling comes from the phone receiver."
    "Se oyen más gritos por el auricular."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:35
translate spanish dana2_b30f69a4:

    # cw "That's fine. I'll see you tonight then."
    cw "Está bien. Entonces nos vemos esta noche."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:37
translate spanish dana2_e7265cb4:

    # "She hangs up the phone and there's a bang as she slams it against the desk."
    "Cuelga el teléfono y se oye un golpe seco al estrellarlo contra el escritorio."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:38
translate spanish dana2_494fc925:

    # "After a moment, I peek around the corner and see her leaning over with her head buried in her hands, her shoulder shaking as she sobs."
    "Al cabo de un momento, me asomo por la esquina y la veo inclinada con la cabeza entre las manos, con los hombros temblando mientras solloza."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:39
translate spanish dana2_a3b7daec:

    # "I probably should just stay out of it, but I can't help it."
    "Probablemente debería mantenerme al margen, pero no puedo evitarlo."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:40
translate spanish dana2_ca8447bf:

    # "I can't stand to see her upset like this. I have this overwhelming urge to fix things."
    "No soporto verla tan alterada. Siento una necesidad abrumadora de arreglar las cosas."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:43
translate spanish dana2_f041e4b8:

    # "I walk up to her desk and put my hand gently onto her shoulder."
    "Me acerco a su escritorio y le pongo la mano suavemente en el hombro."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:44
translate spanish dana2_fa75bbc3:

    # pc "Are you okay?"
    pc "¿Estás bien?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:46
translate spanish dana2_3619d1fa:

    # "She lifts her head and quickly wipes away her tears."
    "Levanta la cabeza y se seca rápidamente las lágrimas."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:47
translate spanish dana2_a3f56836:

    # voice dana_justfine
    # cw "Yeah, everything's just fine."
    voice dana_justfine
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:49
translate spanish dana2_a794c62f:

    # pc "I sort of overheard your conversation."
    pc "He oído parte de tu conversación."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:50
translate spanish dana2_a97815ff:

    # cw "Oh, did you?"
    cw "Ah, ¿de verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:51
translate spanish dana2_efb33164:

    # "She stays silent for a moment, obviously trying to calm herself down."
    "Se queda en silencio un momento, obviamente tratando de calmarse."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:54
translate spanish dana2_391aa753:

    # "Then suddenly everything seems to burst and she wraps her arms around my waist and buries her face into my stomach."
    "De repente, todo parece estallar y me rodea la cintura con los brazos, hundiendo la cara en mi estómago."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:55
translate spanish dana2_458c8244:

    # voice dana_sofrustrated
    # cw "I'm sorry, [pcname]. I'm just so frustrated with all of it."
    voice dana_sofrustrated
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:57
translate spanish dana2_8921cee5:

    # "I put a hand on her back and rub gently as she cries into my shirt."
    "Le pongo una mano en la espalda y le froto suavemente mientras llora sobre mi camisa."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:58
translate spanish dana2_77fb0dd9:

    # "After a couple minutes of sobbing, she starts to calm down again and she pulls back away from me."
    "Tras un par de minutos de sollozos, empieza a calmarse de nuevo y se aparta de mí."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:61
translate spanish dana2_213acdac:

    # cw "I'm sorry. I got your shirt wet."
    cw "Lo siento. Te he mojado la camisa."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:62
translate spanish dana2_45a788d3:

    # pc "It'll dry. Feeling better now?"
    pc "Se secará. ¿Te sientes mejor ahora?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:63
translate spanish dana2_5c9ff614:

    # "She nods."
    "Asiente con la cabeza."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:64
translate spanish dana2_3bb01968:

    # cw "Better. Not great, but better."
    cw "Mejor. No genial, pero mejor."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:65
translate spanish dana2_f02c67f3:

    # cw "I'll figure everything out. I'll get my work done faster and get home earlier, so he won't be mad at me."
    cw "Lo resolveré todo. Terminaré mi trabajo más rápido y llegaré a casa antes, así no se enfadará conmigo."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:66
translate spanish dana2_6831ff3c:

    # pc "If you need anybody to talk to, I'm here okay?"
    pc "Si necesitas a alguien con quien hablar, aquí estoy, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:67
translate spanish dana2_0518d8da:

    # cw "Thanks, [pcname]. You're so sweet."
    cw "Gracias, [pcname]. Eres un encanto."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:68
translate spanish dana2_786b3b21:

    # voice dana_beokay
    # cw "I'll be okay though. I'll see you tomorrow, okay?"
    voice dana_beokay
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:70
translate spanish dana2_d8858bda:

    # pc "Want me to stay and help with anything?"
    pc "¿Quieres que me quede y te ayude con algo?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:71
translate spanish dana2_af71dcbc:

    # cw "That's okay. I got it. Thank you though, really."
    cw "No hace falta. Lo tengo controlado. Pero gracias de verdad."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:72
translate spanish dana2_859c6cd6:

    # pc "Okay, well I'll see you tomorrow then."
    pc "Vale, pues nos vemos mañana."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:73
translate spanish dana2_0507fc22:

    # "I give her a final pat on her shoulder before turning and walking outside. I hope she'll be okay. It's a lot to deal with."
    "Le doy una última palmada en el hombro antes de darme la vuelta y salir. Espero que esté bien. Es mucho con lo que lidiar."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:74
translate spanish dana2_2199c3c0:

    # "I walk through the cool night and get in my car."
    "Camino por la fresca noche y me subo al coche."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:2
    old "Dana has been running late getting home from work."
    new "Dana se está retrasando al volver a casa del trabajo."

    # game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:3
    old "This scene will happen automatically a few days after the previous scene."
    new "Esta escena tendrá lugar automáticamente unos días después de la escena anterior."

